    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'Red pandas are endangered animals facing habitat loss,

    forest fragmentation,
    and other threats in the wild.


    Panda Pause was inspired by a love of red
    pandas and

    the idea that small moments of care can matter.


    As Panda
    Pause grows, we hope to support organizations

    working to protect red pandas
    and their habitats.


    Thank you for being part of that journey.'
