    m_FontStyle: 0
    m_BestFit: 0
    m_MinSize: 1
    m_MaxSize: 40
    m_Alignment: 4
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'Sara is your red panda companion.


    Panda Pause was created to help
    people slow down,

    reflect on their day, and remember the moments that

    matter.


    Sara
    remembers what you share and gently checks in

    with you over time.


    Your
    memories stay on your device and are never

    shared with anyone.


    Panda
    Pause was inspired by a love of red pandas

    and aims to support red panda
    conservation efforts.'
