  m_Text: 'Panda Pause is designed to be private.


    Your journal entries and
    memories stay on your device.


    Panda Pause does not require an account.


    Panda
    Pause does not upload your memories to a server.


    Panda Pause does not sell
    your personal information.


    If you delete your profile or clear your memories,

    that
    data is removed from this device.'
